	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Verdict:<br /><br />1) The fan inside the case was reverted! It was corrected to flow the air from inside to outside.<br />2) The thermal paste was gone. New paste was applied.<br />3) The heatsink was loose. It's fixed.<br />4) One cable had bad placement inside the case.<br /><br />The PC is working like a charm. ^_^;;

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


